6/comment/34680","id":"34680","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=swathi","name":"swathi","key":"swathi","accountId":"557058:ab7e71b5-781c-49ea-9f4d-ea9148c88f03","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Swathi Gangisetty","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"As a part of EUCA-3597, implemented a timeout on tgtadm commands only when attach volume is requested. There are other operations (such as bootstrapping) that rely on tgtadm commands and are vulnerable to tgtd failures. \n\nFix involved extending the previous implementation to all tgtadm commands. Fix is in dev/swathi/EUCA-4040 and is currently running through qa sequences.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=swathi","name":"swathi","key":"swathi","accountId":"557058:ab7e71b5-781c-49ea-9f4d-ea9148c88f03","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Swathi Gangisetty","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2012-11-03T12:49:27.236-0500","updated":"2012-11-03T12:49:27.236-0500"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/16846/comment/34716","id":"34716","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=swathi","name":"swathi","key":"swathi","accountId":"557058:ab7e71b5-781c-49ea-9f4d-ea9148c88f03","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Swathi Gangisetty","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"Code fix commit: 7eb42503f85760c81e2c7fb1d0d7f4e3e6237447\r\n\r\nRoot cause:  tgtadm can hang and cause a storage related operation in Eucalyptus to wait indefinitely \r\n\r\nFix: Extended the implementation for EUCA-3597 to all tgtadm calls. Any process involving an unresponsive (based on a configurable timeout) tgtadm operation will be aborted and a fault will be logged.\r\n\r\nTested the fix using a rogue tgtadm binary that pretends to be unresponsive. When Eucalyptus service are brought up, the SC is in BROKEN state. As the SC tries to transition to ENABLED or DISABLED state, an infinite loop of retries to initialize the storage backend is observed. During the process the SC can be seen transitioning through BROKEN-INITIALIZED-BROKEN states","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=swathi","name":"swathi","key":"swathi","accountId":"557058:ab7e71b5-781c-49ea-9f4d-ea9148c88f03","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Swathi Gangisetty","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2012-11-05T17:18:21.826-0600","updated":"2012-11-05T17:18:21.826-0600"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/16846/comment/35058","id":"35058","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=swathi","name":"swathi","key":"swathi","accountId":"557058:ab7e71b5-781c-49ea-9f4d-ea9148c88f03","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Swathi Gangisetty","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"Replaced the tgtadm binary with a script to imitate tgtd service in a hung state. Brought up a fresh Eucalyptus installation and observed that the SC is in \"BROKEN\" state while constantly (re)trying to initialize. A fault is recorded in the sc-fault.log every time a tgtadm command is unresponsive and the logs clearly record the failed operation.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=swathi","name":"swathi","key":"swathi","accountId":"557058:ab7e71b5-781c-49ea-9f4d-ea9148c88f03","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Swathi Gangisetty","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2012-11-12T16:23:14.182-0600","updated":"2012-11-12T16:23:14.182-0600"}],"maxResults":5,"total":5,"startAt":0},"customfield_11808":null,"worklog":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":20,"total":1,"worklogs":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/16846/worklog/11200","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=swathi","name":"swathi","key":"swathi","accountId":"557058:ab7e71b5-781c-49ea-9f4d-ea9148c88f03","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/d6487612d6674329ecef11be0a95552b?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dswathi%26avatarId%3D17901%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayNa